node.text:
So many little girls are taught to marry a rich man, I was taught if I became educated and worked hard- I could BE a successful woman. Whatever you tell your children, they’ll believe, whatever you tell yourself, you’ll become ✨ Inspire your kids to be great, they deserve that from you. Thank you to my parents for reminding me every single day of how capable I am, and how great I will be. I am me because of you. 
❤️ Pajamas by @nadinemerabi - Photos by @irmalomidze
